			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>In one LDoN hard adventure, I would mez mobs and then fade but they'd still come after mez wore off.  I assumed it was an issue related to fade and mez, but it turns out the cleric was healing me before I faded, so that's why the mob still came.  If mobs are still coming even after you fade, there's an excellent chance someone else in the group had aggro before you faded.
<br />

<br />
