				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: problems lulling in hard ldon<a name="23273"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 23 04 4:21 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>&quot;BE ADVISED if you fade with mobs mezzed then go back to camp with the remains, YOU HAVE NOT LOST AGGRO on the mezzed mob. &quot;
<br />

<br />
As Steppy says, as written this statement is not true.  A couple possible explanations of what's happening.
<br />

<br />
1.  Cleric healed you before you faded -- just like Calli said.
<br />

<br />
2.  You never turned mez song off, or at least didn't turn it off before fading.  If the server ticks and you remez a mob after fading, you get new agro.  
<br />

<br />
However, if you mez a mob, stop mez song, leave agro radius of that mob, and hit fade, you have lost agro.</span></td>
