				<td colspan="2"><span>Well I have never had that happen.  Monday night, after this thread started, I was doing a hard LDON in Mistmoore.  I was in a room that had been cleared.  I had a wanderer coming through the door which I mezzed.  Two mobs behind the wanderer ran in.  I faded and then mezzed one of the two adds.  The wanderer in the door never agrod.
<br />

<br />
What I have found in about one year of having FM is that every single time I THOUGHT there was a bug or that FM had somehow failed, I had actually done something to get agro -- whether it was someone else casting heal or a buff on me or me being in range of a see-invis mob, or whatever -- in every single case where I thought FM was not working right, it wasn't FM that was messing up - it was me or my group.</span></td>
