				<td colspan="2"><span>Haven't researched my songs that high, but I know that my enchanter at 55 doesn't have any memblurs that are 100%. I would assume that the bard doesn't either. That means sometimes it will blur, sometimes it won't. The higher the mob is, the more likely it won't. I know they were working on an issue where neither FD nor memblur were clearing aggro quite like they wanted, but it has been quite well known that neither technique was guaranteed to work 100% for any mob over level 35.
<br />
I have problems using lull in hard missions with both my enc and my bard. My enc's CHA is 255 so I rarely have critical fails, but it does fail.</span></td>
