				<td colspan="2"><span>Read up on farming the Trial of Flame in PoJ for ornate sceptres and the mask of contemplation.  Grats--you now have money, and can buy ornate boots (or slime boots) and 65 mez.
<br />

<br />
Don't do this till 65, but all you really need is 3 dots and PoV.
<br />

<br />
Plus the mask if another FT1.
<br />

<br />
I started pulling hards at FT4 (earing of solstice, of course, plus boots of flowing slime) and am now up to FT7+Mc1.
<br />

<br />
I have more than enough mana regen to competently pull a hard every time.
<br />

<br />
And no, you absolutely do NOT get mobs re-aggro'ing after a fade unless you do something to re-aggro, just as Steppy said.  He is, as usual, quite correct.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
